text: Fatehnagar is a suburb in Hyderabad, Telangana. There are many small scale industries in the area. It is located next to Begumpet Airport. ==Transport== There is a local train station of MMTS, Fateh Nagar Railway Station.Bus stand is even available ==References== Category:Neighbourhoods in Hyderabad, India
title: Fateh Nagar, Hyderabad
